<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Boaz Weinstein and his group of bidders revise=
d their offer to buy Sculptor Capital Management Inc., seeking to address s=
ome of the concerns the board=E2=80=99s special committee outlined in a pro=
