<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In the consumer tech world it is pretty common=
 for a company to start with a popular product but no revenue model. =E2=80=
=9CWe will build an app to let people share pictures with their friends, fo=
r free=E2=80=9D is an idea that can be worth billions of dollars even if it=
 doesn=E2=80=99t make any money. Because, you know, at this point, there is=
 a pretty good history of people finding ways to make it make money. Ads, m=
ainly. Eventually you get to critical mass and you charge companies to adve=
rtise to the people sharing pictures with their friends. This does not alwa=
ys work, but it works often enough and in big enough ways that people keep =
doing it.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You see it less in=C2=A0<em>banking?=C2=A0</em=
